quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  19,66,"Kandi umuntu (w’umuhakanyi) aravuga ati \"Ese nindamuka mpfuye, nzazurwa mbe muzima"
  19,67,"Ese umuntu ntiyibuka ko mbere y’ibyo, ari twe twamuremye kandi ntacyo yari cyo"
  19,68,"Ndahiye (ku izina rya) Nyagasani wawe! Rwose tuzabakoranya (abahakana izuka) hamwe n’amashitani, hanyuma tubazane ku nkengero z’umuriro wa Jahanamu bapfukamye"
  19,69,Hanyuma rwose muri buri gatsiko tuzakuremo abarushije abandi kwigomeka kuri (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe (ari bo babanza guhanwa)
  19,70,"Hanyuma mu by’ukuri, ni twe tuzi neza abakwiye kwinjira mu muriro kurusha abandi"
  19,71,Nta n’umwe muri mwe utazayinyuraho (Siratwa74); iryo ni ihame ntakuka rya Nyagasani wawe
  19,72,"Hanyuma tuzarokore babandi batinye (Allah, bayinyureho), maze tureke inkozi z’ibibi (zigwe mu muriro) zipfukamye"
  19,73,"N’iyo (abantu) basomewe amagambo yacu asobanutse, abahakanye babwira abemeye bati \"Ese ni irihe tsinda muri aya yombi (abahakanye n’abemeye) rirusha irindi urwego rikanarirusha icyicaro cyiza"
  19,74,"Nonese ni ibisekuru bingahe twarimbuye mbere yabo (abahakanyi bo ku gihe cy’intumwa Muhamadi), byabarushaga ibikoresho no kugaragara neza"
  19,75,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Umuntu uri mu buyobe, (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe azamwongerera igihe (cyo gukomeza kuba muri ubwo buyobe) kugeza ubwo bazabona ibyo basezeranyijwe, byaba ibihano (ku isi) cyangwa imperuka. Ubwo nibwo bazamenya ufite umwanya mubi (ubuturo bubi) cyane n’ufite ingabo z’inyantege nke"
  19,76,Kandi Allah yongerera kuyoboka babandi bayobotse. Naho ibikorwa byiza bihoraho ni byo bitanga ingororano n’iherezo Nyagasani wawe. ryiza kwa
  19,77,"Ese wabonye wawundi wahakanye amagambo yacu, maze akavuga ati \"Rwose (ku munsi w’imperuka) nzahabwa imitungo n’urubyaro"
  19,78,Ese yaba yaramenye ibyihishe (akabona ko azahabwa imitungo n’urubyaro)? Cyangwa yagiranye isezerano na (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe (ry’uko azabihabwa)
  19,79,"Siko bimeze! Ahubwo tuzandika ibyo avuga, maze tuzamwongerere ibihano"
  19,80,"Kandi tuzamuzungura ibyo avuga (imitungo n’urubyaro), maze atugereho ari wenyine"
  19,81,"Banishyiriyeho ibigirwamana (barabisenga) baretse Allah, kugira ngo bibarinde (ibihano bya Allah) kandi bibaheshe icyubahiro"
  19,82,"Siko bimeze! Ahubwo (ibyo bigirwamana) bizahakana uko kubisenga kwabo, maze bibabere abanzi (ku munsi w’imperuka)"